{"tid":1138251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[COYS - 最後直路] 熱刺球迷吹水區 139","createTime":"2019-05-04T11:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T11:54:53.000Z","uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"72a16ce2ca264bbd85ab5e661ac6d1548114f519","tid":1138251,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/2L2ISp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L2ISp1&h=6c46b7af&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OME</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">O</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">N</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Y</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OU</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>S</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">PURS</span></span><img src=\"https://bit.ly/2L2ISp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L2ISp1&h=6c46b7af&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZtPVnTAh3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnZtPVnTAh3s&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8QNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=cfadf30c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZtPVnTAh3s</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L68s3aO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL68s3aO.png&h=a977e07d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4YvWaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4YvWaC.jpg&h=67c51792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2Pkn4Z1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pkn4Z1&h=f841e172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/022840_e6a7dfedfa06095191c0abd45e02d012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F022840_e6a7dfedfa06095191c0abd45e02d012.jpg&h=40e1dde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/165211_69f1fc0bfe71d0e7fa1907c235661818.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F165211_69f1fc0bfe71d0e7fa1907c235661818.gif&h=15d6340c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熱刺</span></span></strong>是一間座落英國倫敦北部托定咸區的職業足球會<br />\n從1882年成立至今已經擁有過百年歷史，現時競逐於英格蘭超級聯賽；<br />\n球會主場為熱刺球場，球會的拉丁文格言 &rdquo;<em>Audere est Facere (To Dare Is To Do)</em>&rdquo; 則意謂「<em>敢作敢為</em>」</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">榮譽：</div></strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">甲組聯賽 冠軍：1950/1951、1960/1961<br />\n足總盃 冠軍：1900/1901、1920/1921、1960/1961、1961/1962、1966/1967、1980/1981、1981/1982、1990/1991<br />\n聯賽盃 冠軍：1970/1971、1972/1973、1998/1999、2007/2008<br />\n歐洲盃賽冠軍盃 冠軍：1962/1963<br />\n歐洲足協杯 冠軍：1971/1972、1983/1984<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">賽馬會傑志中心挑戰盃 冠軍：2017/2018<br />\n國際冠軍盃 冠軍：2018/2019<br />\n</span></span><br />\n</div>"}]}